name: Gordon Shumway
description: Gordon "ALF" Shumway is the protagonist and title character of the American television series ALF. He is an alien from the planet Melmac who has arrived on planet Earth, and lands in the Tanner family's garage. Black and white digital sketch. Made for Inktober 2018 on Ibis Paint X on a Samsung Galaxy Tab S3. 2048 x 2048 @350 dpi.
